  "detailed_description": "<strong>Turn platforming on its head with The Gravity Trickster!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778900/extras/454563a786f66c398469d53a48aebb4a.avif?t=1721299752\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br>Defy gravity and traverse tricky 3D platforms and mind-bending challenges as you navigate your robot to the end of each level, collecting keys, coins, cosmic cubes and more as you go! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778900/extras/836d3a064f219198a31b467c39f57989.avif?t=1721299752\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br>Can you find and beat the elusive bonus levels?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778900/extras/1258d6f899b2dbe9bfd5ac15a182277a.avif?t=1721299752\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Each level has been meticulously crafted and rewards creative use of the innovative gameplay mechanics, such as changing gravity.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778900/extras/9361b450de2fd56a4dbf36d057d62ff0.avif?t=1721299752\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br>With regular checkpoints and a 'No Stress' mode The Gravity Trickster is easy to learn and challenging to master. How fast can you clear each stage?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778900/extras/ec7a9b344707ef234dd982a5786826d3.avif?t=1721299752\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778900/extras/5bf89cc00010a40719dce68748286eea.avif?t=1721299752\" width=600 height=210 /></span><br><br>Unlock new cosmetics to customise your robot, including hidden skins and animations for finishing everything!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778900/extras/3ab41b5a109360f4030a23c382dcfef4.avif?t=1721299752\" width=600 height=140 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Turn platforming on its head with The Gravity Trickster!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778900/extras/454563a786f66c398469d53a48aebb4a.avif?t=1721299752\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br>Defy gravity and traverse tricky 3D platforms and mind-bending challenges as you navigate your robot to the end of each level, collecting keys, coins, cosmic cubes and more as you go! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778900/extras/836d3a064f219198a31b467c39f57989.avif?t=1721299752\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br>Can you find and beat the elusive bonus levels?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778900/extras/1258d6f899b2dbe9bfd5ac15a182277a.avif?t=1721299752\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Each level has been meticulously crafted and rewards creative use of the innovative gameplay mechanics, such as changing gravity.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778900/extras/9361b450de2fd56a4dbf36d057d62ff0.avif?t=1721299752\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br>With regular checkpoints and a 'No Stress' mode The Gravity Trickster is easy to learn and challenging to master. How fast can you clear each stage?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778900/extras/ec7a9b344707ef234dd982a5786826d3.avif?t=1721299752\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778900/extras/5bf89cc00010a40719dce68748286eea.avif?t=1721299752\" width=600 height=210 /></spa